  "description": "A medium sized bird with a red cap on a black and white head. There was a black ring around the bill and the bird had a pale eye. The upper breast was black and streaked. There were white spots on the wings that were clearly visible when the bird flew. The bird's rump was white.Behavior: The bird landed on a dead tree that had numerous holes drilled into it. It pecked at the tree several times and then flew to a lower brach where it perched again and then flew off.Call: None heardPlumage: Adult",
